        dc:description           "Figures 7 - 10. 7 Archaeoteleia gracilis, male (OSUC 163002), mesosoma, lateral view 8 Archaeoteleia gracilis, male (OSUC 163002), pronotum and mesopleuron, posterolateral view 9 Archaeoteleia araucana, male paratype (OSUC 163001), head, mesosoma, metasoma, lateral view 10 Archaeoteleia astropulvis, head, mesosoma, metasoma, lateral view. Scale bars in millimeters." , "Figures 3 - 6. 3 Archaeoteleia mellea, female (OSUC 203348), head and antennae, anterior view 4 A. pygmea, female (146602), head and antennae, anterior view 5 Archaeoteleia astropulvis, female holotype (USNMENT 01109982), fore wing and metatibia, dorsal view 6 Archaeoteleia gracilis, male (OSUC 163002), fore wing venation. Scale bars in millimeters." , "Figure 2. Archaeoteleia astropulvis, female holotype (USNMENT 01109982), habitus, dorsolateral view. Scale bars in millimeters." , "Figure 1. Archaeoteleia astropulvis, female holotype (USNMENT 01109982), habitus, ventrolateral view. Scale bars in millimeters." ;
